<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٣ - الْإِيمَان <span style="color:#008000">(الْإِسْلَام)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>أ. الطريف، يُوسُف عَليّ عبد الله <span style="color:#008000">(مُحَقّق)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
